      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 214483948,
      "version": 501,
      "versionNonce": 1588557524,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774013388537,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "JWT is always passed in header of the request in Authentication.\n\nChallenges with JWT :\n1) Token invalidation : If one user is blacklisted, how to invalidate before token expiry\n   a) Server needs to keep list of blacklisted tokens and then DB/cache lookup to validate\n   b) Change the secret key, but this will invalidate for all users.\n   c) token should be very shortlived\n   d) Token should be used only once.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 218,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "JWT is always passed in header of the request in Authentication.\n\nChallenges with JWT :\n1) Token invalidation : If one user is blacklisted, how to invalidate before token expiry\n   a) Server needs to keep list of blacklisted tokens and then DB/cache lookup to validate\n   b) Change the secret key, but this will invalidate for all users.\n   c) token should be very shortlived\n   d) Token should be used only once.\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
